        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8778",
        "content": "One day the little man did not appear, but soon after his usual time the still more gnome like form of his little niece came scrambling rather than walking over the meadow.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
