        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8778",
        "content": "\"It is time, my hearers,\" he said, \"because it is now possible, to bring to a close that uncertainty with regard to the continuance of our relation to each other, which I was, in the spring time of the year, compelled by mental circumstance to occasion.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
